        1/6/2011
    

I didn't know anything about financial investments or what i needed for the future. Jimmy met with me and he understood what i needed to invest in and what I didn't.  He's very honest and made me see the reality of things, such as what will happen in the near future and how i should prepare, cuz let's face it, we all need to prepare for ourself, our future, and for our family. i told him since im still pretty young do i need all this? but it's true, he made me realize the younger you start, it'll be more affordable and easier so in the long run the payout is higher. He was definitely not pushy AT ALL surprisingly, cuz i've met w/other advisors before, and they will always sell you plans or things that you don't need nor ever heard of. And, they don't really know what they're talking about where everything sounds like they're reciting out of a book. I had concerns whether a 401K or IRA will benefit me more and Jimmy was very knowledgeable and actually seemed to care. Very easy to talk to, and consistent. This company really has alot of options to choose from.




        Was this review …?
    







